      "updated": 1776575262207,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ai analyses the photo,\nextracts the information\nand saves that(Which which\ninformation(maybe reverse\nengineer) and how to save\nthat, this system you know\nbetter how to set that up.)",
      "fontSize": 11.660295486927916,
