    {
      "id": "M_O-1L2UFcmj55vUQpvL7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -342.572876242609,
      "y": 1505.1721941906396,
      "width": 190.49876265170997,
      "height": 232.30301501037337,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b06",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 551044815,
      "version": 1961,
      "versionNonce": 1875842351,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776575288195,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now Ai have the successors\nimage/images data, user's\nproduct image/images, its\nown skills/brain/experties to\nask multiple expert\nquestions, dividing the parts\nto get more clear visions. \n\nAbout parts, you may say\nthat part or divisions or\nstages, i dont know but that\nfor the further development\nof the final prompt, you\ngives user to test with the ",
      "fontSize": 13.274458000592764,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now Ai have the successors image/images data, user's product image/images, its own skills/brain/experties to ask multiple expert questions, dividing the parts to get more clear visions. \n\nAbout parts, you may say that part or divisions or stages, i dont know but that  for the further development of the final prompt, you gives user to test with the ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "C2xIqtagFAG6VRyhYFSHp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1110.721734094583,
      "y": 1502.3718624422156,
      "width": 190.49876265170997,
      "height": 547.5713925244515,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b06V",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 523774127,
      "version": 2756,
      "versionNonce": 1831285601,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776575149613,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now Ai have the similar\nimage/images data, user's\nproduct image/images, its\nown skills/brain/experties to\nask multiple expert\nquestions, dividing the parts\nto get more clear visions. \n\nAbout parts, you may say\nthat part or divisions or\nstages, i dont know but that\nfor the further development\nof the final prompt, you\ngives user to test with the.\n\nThe thing to take care is of\nthe similarity level. There are\nmain problems comes with the\noutput of the image, mostly\nuser gets angry on not\ngetting the correct\nreplacement of the product.\nOther instructions are well\nexplained in the Option B,\nfor the prompt creation and\nthe model. But let me tell\nyou again here, that model\nlike \"fal-\nai/bytedance/seedream/v5/li\nte/edit\", will take the\nimage/images, and needs\nperfect prompt to make the\nmockup/mockups.",
      "fontSize": 13.274458000592764,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now Ai have the similar image/images data, user's product image/images, its own skills/brain/experties to ask multiple expert questions, dividing the parts to get more clear visions. \n\nAbout parts, you may say that part or divisions or stages, i dont know but that  for the further development of the final prompt, you gives user to test with the.\n\nThe thing to take care is of the similarity level. There are main problems comes with the output of the image, mostly user gets angry on not getting the correct replacement of the product. Other instructions are well explained in the Option B, for the prompt creation and the model. But let me tell you again here, that model like \"fal-ai/bytedance/seedream/v5/lite/edit\", will take the image/images, and needs perfect prompt to make the mockup/mockups.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
