      "updated": 1776575149613,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "After finalising, an option to\nsave it as a template. if yes\nthen with the last image\ngenerated and the prompt used\nfor it the template will be\ncreated. For M1 and M2\nseparately.",
      "fontSize": 9.076827955812037,
